title: Temple of Riellis
story: The temple of Riellis is situated at the center of a lake. These days it is overrun with spiders.

notes.text: A relief, totally destroyed by kobold vandals.
A creepy bony elf. Wants to join you.
A dying druid, a key among his belongings.
A notable stone door with a keyhole on the eastern wall.
A magic wand in the middle of a circle of runes on the ground.
A statue of a dwarf, heals a person when touched.
A large strongbox holds a silver chain.
